    <p>MATTEO BOCELLI: He knows that he's had tough way.</p>
    <p>KELLY: That's Matteo Bocelli and his father, Andrea Bocelli, talking about their song "Fall On Me." I talked to them both with the help of a translator about what it means to record together.</p>
