    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED RECORDING)</p>
    <p>FITZGERALD: I am committed to seeing this change process through.</p>
    <p>BOOKER: Fitzgerald declined to be interviewed for this story. He was scheduled to have a confirmation hearing next week, but it was postponed due to a family emergency.</p>
