    <p>FULLER: And you had to do what they said. If you didn't, your hide.</p>
    <p>DOTSON: You kept your mouth shut. If you didn't, they'd fire you. So I just kept my mouth shut and went on. But I paid for it in the long run. Sure have. And I'm sure every other miner has too.</p>
    <p>KELLY: Just almost every guy that I know in our church was a coal miner. My pastor, he had black lung. Bill has black lung. Mike had black lung.</p>
    <p>SPARKS: My father-in-law...</p>
