    <p>SUGAHARA: Hi. Good morning. How are you?</p>
    <p>GONZALEZ: Principal Sugahara says she hopes the new agreement means more resources for her school.</p>
    <p>SUGAHARA: There are a lot of families that go through trauma, so we need more in terms of social, emotional support. Good morning. How are you? Hi, Alexa (ph). Hi, Nate (ph). Thank you. So I think it varies. I think every school is different. I think that for our school, we would benefit from a five-day-a-week nurse. That would benefit us.</p>
