    <p>MARY LOUISE KELLY, HOST: </p>
    <p>Our co-host Ari Shapiro reported yesterday from the small town of Oakdale, La. And one of the voices he brought us was Nathan Dyer. He is a prison worker whose young son has a birthday today. Here he is.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED BROADCAST)</p>
