    <p>President Trump puts the odds of striking a deal at, quote, less than 50/50. Yesterday we asked a Democrat on the conference committee, Congressman David Price of North Carolina, about the president's remarks.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF ARCHIVED BROADCAST)</p>
